GET
/groups/{GroupID}
Get group


This method returns the group metadata with all information about the group and its participants

Parameters
Name	Description
GroupID *
string
(path)
Group ID

GroupID
Responses
Code	Description	Links
200	
OK

Media type

application/json
Controls Accept header.
Example Value
Schema
{
  "id": "283642-086620294@mZN",
  "name": "Group name",
  "type": "group",
  "timestamp": 1675964377,
  "chat_pic": "https://example.com/photo.jpg",
  "chat_pic_full": "https://example.com/photo.jpg",
  "pin": true,
  "mute": true,
  "mute_until": 0,
  "archive": true,
